ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/11519/documentation

This dataset represents the production of 3/8-inch (9,5mm) oriented strand board in Quebec and is collected from four different mills in Canada between 2005 and 2006. ;The dataset is based on Canadian average but is representative of Quebec's production.

Activity starts at the entrance of the production site. it includes:
- the inputs (materials and energy) to the production processes received at the factory gate;
- the infrastructures (building, furnace for wood).


Activity ends at the gate of the production site. Outputs include:
- the material outputs (oriented strand borad and by-products);
- process emissions;
- combustion emissions from wood (internal use).
